"use strict";(self.webpackChunkjava_note_vuepress2=self.webpackChunkjava_note_vuepress2||[]).push([[950],{13355:(a,s,n)=>{n.r(s),n.d(s,{data:()=>e});const e={key:"v-5210f009",path:"/html/02-%E5%8D%95%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0.html",title:"单标签元素与双标签元素",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[],filePathRelative:"html/02-单标签元素与双标签元素.md",git:{updatedTime:1629711344e3,contributors:[{name:"hemiao",email:"hemiao3000@126.com",commits:1}]}}},38294:(a,s,n)=>{n.r(s),n.d(s,{default:()=>t});const e=(0,n(66252).uE)('<h1 id="单标签元素与双标签元素" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#单标签元素与双标签元素" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 单标签元素与双标签元素</h1><p>HTML 中的元素分为 <strong>单标签元素</strong> 和 <strong>双标签元素</strong> 。</p><blockquote><p>在 HTML 中，<code>&lt;xxx&gt;</code> 被称为 XXX 元素的 <strong>开始标签</strong>，相对应的，<code>&lt;/xxx&gt;</code> 则被称为 xxx 元素的结束标签。</p><p>在 XML 的语法规则中，实际上并没有单标签元素，只有双标签元素。</p></blockquote><p>单标签元素只用一个标签符号既可描述某个功能，其语法如下：</p><div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>标签名</span> <span class="token punctuation">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>例如：</p><div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>hr</span> <span class="token punctuation">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><blockquote><p><small>在严格的语法规则中，标签名和 / 之间要求有一个空格。</small></p></blockquote><p>双标签元素则需要两个标签符号（开始标签和结束标签）来描述某个功能，其如法如下：</p><div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>标签名</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>内容<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>标签名</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>上面所说的 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;body&gt;</code> 很显然都是双标签元素。</p>',11),t={render:function(a,s){return e}}}}]);